Dxf2Svg Description:

Dxf2Svg converts Autodesk AutoCAD's defacto standard Drawing eXchange Format (DXF) into a Scaleable Vector Graphic (SVG). It is a stand alone file format converter written in Java (available from Sun Microsystems Inc.).
